A Presentation View for PDF Presentations based on PyQt4 and Poppler

Needs pypoppler-qt4, get it here:
http://pyqt4-extrawidgets.googlecode.com/files/pypoppler-qt4-20962-fixed.tar.gz
and install:
python configure.py
make
sudo make install

Usage:
1. Run: python pdfpresenter.py
2. Focus on black window
3. Press 'o' to open a file
4. Move presentation view to projector/external display
5. Press 'f' to enter fullscreen mode
6. Wait for caching to finish
7. Use right/left arrow keys to go to next/previous slide

